dc_title_s: Geologic map of the Orchard Peak quadrangle, San Luis Obispo & Kern Counties, California
dc_description_s: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle ORCHARD PEAK, CA 1961, REVISED 1993." "First printing, February 2005." Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology. Includes "pertinent references."
dc_publisher_s: Santa Barbara Museum of Natural History
